      • FurnishingClassifier

        public FurnishingClassifier(java.lang.String[] inputPaths)
        classifies only three categories, wall-paper, wooden-floor, floor-tile
        In python the corresponding classifier is HardwareClassifier         分类3类贴图：墙纸、墙砖、地板， 对应python为HardwareClassifier
        参数:
        inputPaths - paths to all inputs. if first element of this array is a dir, the result file is saved there; if not, the result file is saved alongside with this file 如果该数组的第一个元素是文件夹， 结果列表储存在该文件夹中，否则储存在第一个文件所在的文件夹中
